        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Intro",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing the right necklace for a V-neck outfit can completely elevate your look. Whether you prefer minimal elegance, bold statement pieces, or fine diamond jewellery, understanding <em>what necklace to wear with a V-neck</em> ensures your neckline appears elongated, balanced, and stylish.<br/> This guide also helps you understand what necklace to wear with what neckline and which necklace to wear with which neckline so you can style every outfit with confidence.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the V-Neckline",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the V-Neckline</h2><p>The V-neck is one of the most versatile and universally flattering necklines. It naturally draws the eyes downward, making your neck look longer and adding structure to your outfit.<br/> The right necklace should complement this shape instead of competing with it.</p>",
            "custom_id": "understanding"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BmD46M": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Best Necklaces  Paragaph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Best Necklaces to Wear With a V-Neck</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_kdyBGr": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Best_Necklace_To_Wear_With_V_neck.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Best Necklaces to Wear With a V-Neck",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. Pendant Necklaces</h3><p>Pendant necklaces mirror the pointed structure of the V-neck, creating harmony and balance. They are ideal for both casual and formal looks.</p><h3>2. Drop Necklaces</h3><p>Drop necklaces enhance the elongating effect of the V-neck and work beautifully with deep or narrow V-shapes.</p><h3>3. Layered Necklaces</h3><p>A layered necklace set creates a soft cascading effect that complements shallow V-necks. Keep the layers delicate for a refined look.</p>",
            "custom_id": "best"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_MYCtgW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Matching Necklaces With Different V-Neck Styles",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Matching Necklaces With Different V-Neck Styles</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_86fATf": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Matching_Necklaces_With_Different_V-Neck_Styles.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Matching Necklaces Paragarph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>A. Deep V-Neck</h3><p>A single long pendant, lariat necklace, or drop necklace enhances the vertical line of the neckline.<br/> If you prefer a subtle sparkle, a sleek piece like a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> can add understated glamour.</p><h3>B. Wide V-Neck</h3><p>A shorter pendant necklace or a fine choker helps fill the empty space and draws attention toward your collarbones.<br/> For added sophistication, pair your chosen necklace with classic earrings such as <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-studs\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond studs</span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">.</span></p><h3>C. Soft or Curved V-Neck</h3><p>Soft V-necks look best with necklaces that follow a gentle downward curve—think minimalist pendants or layered chains.<br/> This pairing works beautifully for both casual tops and elegant evening-wear.</p>",
            "custom_id": "matching"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Styling Tips for V-Neck Outfits",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Styling Tips for V-Neck Outfits</h2><h3>1. Match the Metal to the Outfit’s Tone</h3><p>Cool colours pair well with white gold and platinum, while warm shades complement rose gold or yellow gold pieces.</p><h3>2. Keep the Balance Right</h3><p>If you're wearing a heavily embellished V-neck, choose a minimal necklace. For a simple neckline, you can experiment with bolder styles.</p><h3>3. Pair With Complementary Jewellery</h3><p>Your necklace should work harmoniously with other accessories.<br/> For modern styling, explore unique shapes through a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/modern-diamond-earrings-design\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">modern diamond earrings design</span></a> collection.</p><h3>4. Add a Touch of Shine With Bracelets</h3><p>When keeping your necklace simple, adding a bracelet can balance your entire look.<br/> A timeless choice is the <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/diamond-tennis-bracelet\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">diamond tennis bracelet</span></a>.</p>",
            "custom_id": "styling"
          }
        },
